Preserve an explicit ``VALUE`` parameter (for example ``RDATE;VALUE=PERIOD`` or ``TRIGGER;VALUE=DATE-TIME``) when converting from jCal. Previously :meth:`Component.from_jcal <icalendar.cal.component.Component.from_jcal>` dropped the value type, which is encoded in the jCal type field rather than as a parameter. @gaoflow @lcampanella98